 111:linked_list.c **** /*
 112:linked_list.c ****  * Function to get the Morse code representation of a character.
 113:linked_list.c ****  * The function returns a pointer to an array of morse_code values.
 114:linked_list.c ****  * The array is dynamically allocated and should be freed by the caller.
 115:linked_list.c ****  * morse code is formatted as follows:
 116:linked_list.c ****  * - SHORT = dot (·), LONG= dash (−), END = end of character (|)
 117:linked_list.c ****  * - The array is terminated with END.
 118:linked_list.c ****  */
